                  <span class="word blue">✧˚ ༘ ⋆｡♡˚</span>
                  <span class="word red">ଘ(੭ˊ꒳​ˋ)੭✧</span>
                  <span class="word green">⸜(｡˃ ᵕ ˂ )⸝♡</span>
                  <span class="word orange">⸜(*ˊᗜˋ*)⸝</span>
