                 Hi!! I'm a 4th year EE student @ the <a href="https://www.ualberta.ca">university of alberta</a>. Thanks for visiting!
				 Some of my interests include <a href="https://arvp.org">robotics</a>, photography and art. Check out my projects in <a href="/posts?tag=project">posts</a> and my creative work in <a href="/art">art</a>
